      <title>尽管美联储放宽政策，投资者仍连续第四年抛售黄金 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/investors-sell-gold-etfs-for-fourth-year-even-with-fed-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024年，尽管黄金价格屡创新高且美联储开始放松货币政策，但投资者仍连续第四年抛售黄金支持的交易所交易基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/investors-sell-gold-etfs-for-fourth-year-even-with-fed-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 13:16:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国兴业银行的 Juckes 表示，对美元而言，政治因素比经济因素更重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-02/politics-more-important-to-dollar-than-economics-juckes-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国兴业银行首席外汇策略师 Kit Juckes 讨论了他认为未来一年推动美元走势的因素，以及他对美国政治和政策对货币影响的担忧。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-02/politics-more-important-to-dollar-than-economics-juckes-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 12:46:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Tesla、Nvidia 和 AI：Dan Ives 的 2025 年技术预览</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-02/tesla-nvidia-and-ai-dan-ives-2025-tech-preview-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Wedbush 高级股票研究分析师 Dan Ives 预计科技股将在 2025 年上涨 25%，因为他认为大型科技公司和特斯拉将拥有一个黄金时代的基础。他在“彭博监控”上发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-02/tesla-nvidia-and-ai-dan-ives-2025-tech-preview-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 12:33:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>庞氏骗局爆发后，土耳其提议限制银行首席执行官任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/turkey-proposes-limit-on-bank-ceo-tenures-after-ponzi-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其银行业监管机构制定了一项计划，旨在限制银行高管的任期，此前，一家银行的首席执行官被指控涉嫌庞氏骗局，该银行是该国任职时间最长的银行之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/turkey-proposes-limit-on-bank-ceo-tenures-after-ponzi-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 12:18:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国抵押贷款利率升至 7 月初以来最高水平，抑制需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/us-mortgage-rates-rise-to-highest-since-early-july-suppressing-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[圣诞假期期间，美国抵押贷款利率攀升至近六个月高位，抑制了购房申请，并严重削弱了再融资活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/us-mortgage-rates-rise-to-highest-since-early-july-suppressing-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元兑美元跌至 2022 年以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/eur-usd-euro-falls-to-weakest-versus-dollar-since-november-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对欧洲经济及其与美国货币政策分歧的担忧，欧元兑美元跌至两年多以来的最低水平。]]></description>
